The paper deals with the problem of matching images and text, which is a common task in computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and information retrieval (cs.IR). The proposed method involves a novel Multi-modal Tensor Fusion Network (MTFN) and a generic Cross-modal Re-ranking (RR) scheme, which are both related to multi-modal learning (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG).
